      </p><p class="p79 ft14">Lecturers:</p><p class="p79 ft9">
        J M Buys, MSc <span class="ft30">Stell </span>DPhil
        <span class="ft30">Oxon</span>
      </p><p class="p79 ft9">
        J Chavula, MSc <span class="ft30">Lancaster </span>PhD
        <span class="ft30">Cape Town</span>
      </p><p class="p79 ft13">Adjunct Lecturer:</p><p class="p79 ft9">
        M Molapo, MSc PhD <span class="ft30">Cape Town</span>
      </p><p class="p79 ft14">Computer System Managers:</p><p class="p79 ft9">
        C Balfour, BSocSc <span class="ft30">Cape Town </span>BA (SS) Hons
        <span class="ft30">Unisa</span>
