      </p><p class="p79 ft3">
        <span class="ft13">DP requirements: </span>Minimum of 45% aggregate in
        practical work.
      </p><div id="p99dimg1">
        <img src="data:image/png;base64," id="p99img1">
      </div><p class="p559 ft3">
        <span class="ft13">Assessment: </span>Theory tests count 15%; practical
        tests and practical assignments count 25%; one 2-
      </p><p class="p562 ft3">
        hour exam written in November counts 60%. Subminima: 45% for practicals
