        K van der Merwe, HDipEd <span class="ft39">CPUT</span>
      </p><p class="p94 ft14">Principal Technical Officer:</p><p class="p94 ft9">N Bredekamp</p><p class="p94 ft14">Chief Technical Officer:</p><p class="p94 ft12">D September</p><p class="p94 ft14">Senior Technical Officer:</p><p class="p94 ft9"><nobr>---</nobr></p><p class="p94 ft13">Department Manager:</p><p class="p94 ft9">Y L Burrows</p><p class="p94 ft14">Finance Administrator:</p><p class="p94 ft9">
