        <span class="ft12">D</span><span class="ft110">Davids</span>
      </p><p class="p94 ft14">Senior Clerk:</p><p class="p94 ft3">K Jeptha</p><p class="p434 ft13">
        CENTRE FOR STATISTICS IN ECOLOGY, ENVIRONMENT AND CONSERVATION (SEEC)
      </p><p class="p94 ft13">Director:</p><p class="p94 ft12">R Altwegg, PhD <span class="ft39">Zurich</span></p><p class="p94 ft14">Core members<span class="ft9">:</span></p><p class="p94 ft9">
